<br>
This doesn't hurt elemental planes level guilds, it hurts the guilds right below them a fair amount. They've just eliminated all the steps. And for what?<br>
<br>
There a jillion places in the old world that net great experience and loot for people 46-60. Places that are challenging and fun to be in. Most are already deserted, this will only increase that. Moving forward as a guild, completing accomplishments, is a progression. It trains you, it teaches you, it gives you a feeling of accomplishment. I was proud when I won the trials, happy when my guild won against flag mobs, happy for other guilds when they did the same. <br>
<br>
This wasn't elitism, this was progression.<br>
<br>
